Paul B. Toms Jr.       
Executive Compensation
As Chairman and CEO at HOOKER FURNITURE CORP, Paul B. Toms Jr.        made $884,494 in total compensation.  Of this total $407,500 was received as a salary, $186,750 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $249,000 was awarded as stock and $41,244 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2017 fiscal year. 


